Package simu.model.entity

Class RunStatistics

java.lang.Object
simu.model.entity.RunStatistics
@Entity public class RunStatistics extends Object
JPA entity that stores aggregated queue statistics for a single simulation Run. Mapped to the table run_statistics. Each row is associated 1:1 with a Run via a foreign key column run_id (unique, non-null). All metrics are stored as either integer maxima or double-precision averages per queue type.
Author:
Elias Rinne
